<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="light">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>404 — Not Found</title>
    <link phx-track-static rel="stylesheet" href={~p"/assets/css/app.css"} />
    <style>
      :root { --page-bg: #ffffff; }
      body { background: var(--page-bg); color: #000000; }
      .card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="flex mt-5 items-center justify-center min-h-screen">
      <div class="card p-4 text-center shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center" style="max-width:720px;">
        <div class="w-1/4"></div>
        <div class="w-3/4">
          <img
            src="https://i.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/003/015/903/316.png"
            alt="Illustration"
            class="rounded mt-3 mb-3 w-full object-cover"
            style="max-height:320px;"
          />
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-9xl font-bold">404</h1>
        <p class="text-xl">Oh no, you went too far — you found Larry.</p>
        <p class="mb-4">He doesn't usually appreciate visitors in his domain.</p>
        <hr class="my-4 w-full border-gray-300" />
        <small class="text-gray-500">Proceed with caution. Larry is a villainous cat.</small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
